                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370814-1799-offence-1 t18370814-cd-30"></join>28th of July</rs>, 1 handkerchief, value 4<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., the goods of <persName id="t18370814-name-306" type="victimName">
